title: Burnley 1-0 Leicester City: Late Vokes strike seals three points
text:
Burnley 1-0 Leicester City: Late Vokes strike seals three points Getty 0 31 Jan 2017 21:38:51 The Wales striker found the net in the 87th minute to heap more misery on Ranieri's flagging Foxes 
Sam Vokes was the hero for Burnley on Tuesday, scoring late on at Turf Moor to seal all three points and condemn the Premier League champions to yet another defeat. 
More to follow...
